      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   f-ali-pat              .
           string    "/abd/azi/"
                                delimited by size
                     rr-cod-azi delimited by spaces
                     "/"        delimited by size
                     f-xxx-nam  delimited by spaces
                                          into f-ali-pat              .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
