      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      101                  to   ali-ann-fis            .
           move      spaces               to   ali-tip-arc            .
           move      zero                 to   ali-cod-arc            .
           move      zero                 to   ali-cod-iva            .
           move      spaces               to   ali-ann-cop            .
      *
           start     ali    key not less
                            ali-k01
                            invalid key
                            go to exe-cnv-ali-800.
       exe-cnv-ali-250.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Next su [old]                                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           read      ali    next
                            with no lock
                            at end
                            go to exe-cnv-ali-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Incremento numero records letti                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   inc-rec-let-000      thru inc-rec-let-999        .
       exe-cnv-ali-300.
